Package: execpermfix
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fixes executable permissions
 execpermfix sets or resets the executable permission of a file based on its
 name and contents. When setting the permission, only users that can read the
 file will be able to execute it.

